Hey England, good luck this game!
DMZ English Channel?

Hey Austria, best of luck this game!
What are your thoughts on your neighbor to the north?
Hi France, any chance we can agree to DMZ Burgundy? If you stay out of there, then I'll stay out too, and then we can talk about Belgium in the fall.

Hey Germany, best of luck this game!
Any thoughts on our mutual neighbor to the north?
Ah, looks like we're on the same page. Sounds good

Hey Italy, best of luck this game!
DMZ Piedmont, Gol, West Med, and Tyrrhenian?

Hey Russia, best of luck this game!
What are your thoughts on our mutual neighbor to the north? (England)

Hi France! Good luck to you too!

I don't have any information about Germany yet. I've only just gotten here!

Hey Turkey, good luck this game!
We won't have any early interactions, but I'm always happy to have an open line of communication
Ah, no worries. Germany reached out to me, but we haven't talked much. DMZ in Burgundy, but that's all I know
Were you thinking of moving into Tyrolia?
England?

No. I am hoping to convince Italy to work with me, but they haven't responded.

I think I would open to Albania, Galicia, and Serbia.
We both have other neighbors to focus on, so it would be good for both of us to stay out of each other's way
If we're both committed to building fleets, I think we could work together to take them out fairly quickly. Maybe we can get Russia involved as well?
Germany and I are considering going after them. We'd like your help. If you move Moscow to St. Petersburg you could grab Norway and Sweden, and then we'd each have one less neighbor to worry about
Let me know what you think!
The problem with Galicia is that it would almost certainly make Russia mad. But Serbia is yours no matter what
Russia almost never moves to Galicia. It's such a bad move.
Actually, might be worth it. Just make sure Russia doesn't go into Galicia
Oh yeah? I've always been aggressive and tried to move in. Did it once as Austria though
I am going to make sure of that.
Yeah, it's suicide.
Yes? No?
